steps to running the game

1. install the nest cli with the commend
   npm i -g @nestjs/cli
2. install all the needed packages
3. npm start at the xoxo folder

the server of the game will run our game will conduct with postman

1. go the route localhost:3000/getBoard
   and run a get request with no parameters
   it would return you the board

2. then make a post request to route localhost:3000/move
   with the location you want your piece to be
   the request body would look like this in the raw json:
   {
   "x": 0,
   "y": 2
   }

it will switch players automatically and will write you what player is the current turn

to restart the game when finished send empty post request to localhost:3000/restartGame
